…只怪我读书少，无法用华丽的词语来形容它。我举着它，骄傲的站在村口，村都沸腾了，更有人喊，我不给他们看，他们就跳井。吓得我赶紧收起宝贝，挤出人群落荒而逃。为测试宝贝效果，我立刻去我们村高达100米山上村长家客厅里用。用完后，在全村人羡慕的眼光中，昂首挺胸扬长而去……\",\"comment_grade\":1,\"add_time\":\"2018-04-04\",\"up_num\":133,\"down_num\":0,\"reply_content\":\"你又在这里吹牛了。工头到处找你，叫你赶紧回工地去，还有两车水泥要卸，工头说再不回去你那10天300块的工钱一分都别想拿到。还有隔壁如玉去乡里派出所撤案了，说5年前你偷看他洗澡的事情就算了，安心回村里来吧，不要在外面瞎逛、胡说八道了。感谢您对小米的支持。\",\"reply_time\":\"2018-04-05\",\"comment_title\":\"\",\"up_customer_num\":337,\"user_reply_num\":1,\"is_top\":\"1\",\"up_rate\":100,\"average_grade\":5,\"site_id\":\"101\",\"site_name\":\"小米移动商城\",\"comment_images\":[],\"up\":false,\"down\":false,\"has_up_customer\":false,\"user_replys\":[{\"admin_id\":\"343\",\"assigner_id\":\"343\",\"check_time\":\"1522997395\",\"comment_id\":\"155421205\",\"is_delete\":\"0\",\"parent_id\":\"0\",\"reply_content\":\"成义\",\"reply_id\":\"1789102\",\"reply_time\":\"1522973902\",\"status\":\"1\",\"user_avatar\":\"https://cdn.cnbj0.fds.api.mi-img.com/b2c-data-mishop/c52c11c915d43e0ac3286161eec4fcaf.jpg\",\"user_id\":\"133***3390\",\"user_name\":\"1338003390\"}]}],\"total\":677},\"viewType\":\"commentView\"},\"descTabsView\":{\"descTabsView\":[{\"name\":\"概述\",\"tabContent\":[{\"plainView\":{\"content\":\"\",\"img\":\"//i8.mifile.cn/v1/a1/2c387f6d-6c94-4866-5d3d-4e1719d73e07.webp?w=1080&h=1097\",\"is_not_compress\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\"},\"viewType\":\"plainView\"},{\"plainView\":{\"content\":\"\",\"img\":\"//cdn.cnbj0.fds.api.mi-img.com/b2c-mimall-media/fa4a54d4f6b18634647de50da6732d8d.jpg?w=1080&h=777\",\"is_not_compress\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\"},\"viewType\":\"plainView\"},{\"plainView\":{\"content\":\"\",\"img\":\"//i8.mifile.cn/v1/a1/b3fa1446-c07c-2d54-d983-664e50551a12.webp?w=1080&h=1422\",\"is_not_compress\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\"},\"viewType\":\"plainView\"},{\"plainView\":{\"content\":\"\",\"img\":\"//i8.mifile.cn/v1/a1/0c031556-3387-b40f-930c-17f74439b6b5.webp?w=1080&h=1887\",\"is_not_compress\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\"},\"viewType\":\"plainView\"},{\"plainView\":{\"content\":\"\",